parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the headlights can cause reduced visibility, increasing the risk of accidents, especially at night or in low-light conditions.
symptoms: The headlights fail to illuminate
the low beam headlights become inoperable
the headlights intermittently fail
the headlights stall without warning
the automatic headlights fail to function
the daytime running lights fail to operate.

parsedComplaintsResult.issueCategory: Intermittent Airbag Light and Electrical Issues
parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The intermittent airbag light and electrical issues can lead to a failure of the airbag system, which can increase the risk of injury or death in the event of a crash.
symptoms: The airbag light comes on and off
the passenger airbag light is off even when a passenger is seated
the instrument panel display fails to work
and the door locks and radio malfunction.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the headlights can increase the risk of a crash, especially at night or in low-visibility conditions.
symptoms: The headlights fail to turn on
the low beam headlights shut off while driving
and the high beam headlights work properly.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the electrical system can cause a loss of power, leading to a loss of control of the vehicle, which can increase the risk of a crash.
symptoms: The vehicle stalls
the engine shuts off
and the electrical system fails to function properly.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the door lock actuator can cause the doors to become stuck or unlock while driving, which can increase the risk of injury or death.
symptoms: The door locks malfunction
the doors become stuck or unlock while driving
and the remote door locks do not function properly.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the ignition switch can cause the engine to stall, which can increase the risk of a crash.
symptoms: The engine stalls
the vehicle fails to start
and the ignition switch malfunctions.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The malfunction of the airbag system can lead to the failure of the airbags to deploy in the event of an accident, potentially causing serious injury or death.
symptoms: The airbag warning light on the dashboard is illuminated
the passenger airbag light remains off even when the seat is occupied
the airbag readiness indicator is lit
the seatbelt light is on
and the airbag warning light blinks or remains on intermittently.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the passenger airbag sensor can cause the airbag to malfunction, leading to the failure of the airbag to deploy in the event of an accident, potentially causing serious injury or death.
symptoms: The passenger airbag light remains off even when the seat is occupied
the airbag warning light is illuminated
the passenger airbag sensor is faulty
and the airbag readiness indicator is lit.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the airbag control module can cause the airbag system to malfunction, leading to the failure of the airbags to deploy in the event of an accident, potentially causing serious injury or death.
symptoms: The airbag warning light is illuminated
the airbag readiness indicator is lit
and the airbag system is inoperative.
